<dl id="n53050m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n53" href="#n53050m">N53 (VI.B.46)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n53all.htm#n53050m"> 50(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> time organ</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Why is our world &mdash; the way it represents itself in language &mdash; so extremely spatial? Why do we find our bearings faster in three-dimensional space than in unidimensional time? &hellip; Because our visual faculty also serves as a space organ. Because our sense of hearing does not equally serve as a <mark>time organ</mark>.]</font> <small> Fritz Mauthner, <a name="FMBK1" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FMBK1"><cite title="source">Beitr&auml;ge zu einer Kritik der Sprache.</cite></a> 3 vols (1901-2) III 128</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
